Step-01:
Register a domain from freenome. 
Login in mentioned URl from your login credentials.
Here is link: https://my.freenom.com/

Step-02: Register a domain with free nameserver.
nameserver e.g: .tk, ga etc.

Your domain name: abc-test.tk

step-03: Generate SSL certificate for this domain.
Login in mentioned URL.
Here is the link: https://www.sslforfree.com/

Step-04:
Click on create SSL.
Then click on "new certificate" > "Enter Domain" > check on "90-Day Certificate" > click on "next" > click on "next" > 
In Domain verification section select "DNS(CNAME)" > Copy "name" expact domain name and "Point To"
e.g:
Name: _CD8ACBBCFC89647BBFB134F852DB8597.abc-test.tk
Copy only: _CD8ACBBCFC89647BBFB134F852DB8597

Point To:
9315C4378F589C6BB3FAF1CE054E857D.27712FCE4360D831E99BE56D1054A32E.5f146d558b320ce.comodoca.com

Step-05: Login in the freenom. 
Click on "Service" > "My domain" > click on "manage domain" on your domain > "Manage Freenom DNS" > 
In "modify record" click on "name" section and mention your name.
And in "Target" section provide "Point To" details which we have copied in step-04.
After providing "name" and "Target" save it.
e.g:
Name: _CD8ACBBCFC89647BBFB134F852DB8597
Target: 9315C4378F589C6BB3FAF1CE054E857D.27712FCE4360D831E99BE56D1054A32E.5f146d558b320ce.comodoca.com

Step-06:
Go to the below link.
Here is link: https://www.whatsmydns.net/
Paste "_CD8ACBBCFC89647BBFB134F852DB8597.abc-test.tk"
Select "CNAME" then click on search
Note: It will take little time for propagation.
Through this process our Domain name will be verified.

Step-07: 
Now go to the "SSLforFree" link.
Click on "Next" and download certificate.

Step-08:
Convert your certificate into pfx file.

Go to the mentioned link.
Here is the link: https://www.sslshopper.com/ssl-converter.html

Select "Type To Convert To" --> PFX
Upload certificate files according to provided list.

Certificate File to Convert: Upload here certificate file, file name "certificate.crt".
Private Key File: Upload here private key file, file name "private.key".
Chain Certificate File (optional): Upload here chain file, file name "ca_bundle.crt".

After uploading all 3 files. Provide password in "PFX Password" section.
Note: Anything you can provide in password section.

After proving password click on "convert certificate"

It will provide us pfx file.
